title: Day 1212

# Day 1212

Man I love steak. Whole Foods has these pre-seasoned meats they sell which I highly recommend. The carne asada I had for lunch today was delicious. Also they had a pork bulgogi I ate the other day which was incredible.

Amazing how much value you can create with a finished product. Food for thought.

I need to finish my Bitcoin Coloring Book.

7/16/25

Conor Jay Chepenik
